my descendant and all my families including my brothers and all those that their affairs concerns me, (Amen) the Lord of the worlds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA BE-HAQQE WALIYYE-KA WA HUJJATE-KA SAAHE-BIZ ZAMAANE ILLAA A-A’NTA-NEE BEHI A’LAA JAMEE-E’ OMOO-REE, WA KA-FAIY-TANEE BEHI MAOO-NATA KULLE MAUZE WA TAA-GHIN WA BAA-GHIN, WA A-A’NTA-NEE BEHI, FA-QAD BALAGHA MAJ-HOODEE, WA KAFAIY-TANEE KULLA A’DOO-WIN WA HAMMIN (GHAMMIM) WA DAIY-NIN, WA WULDEE WA JAMEE-A’ AHLEE WA IKH-WAANEE, WA MAIY-YO’NEENEE AMRO-HU WA KHAS-SATEE, AAMEENA RABBAL AA’LAMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّيْ اَسْاَلُكَ بِحَقِّ وَلِيِّكَ وَحُجَّتِكَ صَاحِبِ الزَّمَانِ اِلَّا اَعَنْتَنِيْ بِهٖ عَلٰى جَمِيْعِ اُمُوْرِيْ، وَكَفَيْتَنِيْ بِهٖ مَؤُوْنَةَ كُلِّ مُوْذٍ وَطَاغٍ وَبَاغٍ، وَاَعَنْتَنِيْ بِهٖ، فَقَدْ بَلَغَ مَجْهُوْدِيْ، وَكَفَيْتَنِيْ كُلَّ عَدُوٍّ وَهَمٍّ ( َغَمٍّ) وَدَيْنٍ، وَوُلْدِيْ وَجَمِيْعَ اَهْلِيْ وَاِخْوَانِيْ، وَمَن يُّعْنِيْنِيْ اَمْرُهٗ وَخَاصَّتِيْ، اٰمِيْنَ رَبَّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign1